    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概述</h2>《开局一把剑》是一款以技能搭配为核心玩法的Rougelike地牢游戏。玩家通过击败怪物获得装备和技能强化自身，通过合理的配置来击败最终Boss，游戏中存在无尽的可能给与玩家探索。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄</h2>每个英雄拥有自己独特的天赋和成长，配合天赋搭配技能也许是一个比较省心的选择<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355440/extras/b47cfbd7d15ed119b46546d34beb740d.avif?t=1656313626\" width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能</h2>游戏中有超过100个可获得技能，这些技能获得后可以任意组合撘配，进而达到各种不可思议的效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355440/extras/38735b923f1a81f33828f1b7fc9b9363.avif?t=1656313626\" width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装备</h2>装备由系统自动随机生成，优质的装备会含有多个额外的附加属性和技能，合适的装备可以弥补技能搭配的疏漏，从而打造更完美的组合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355440/extras/fa735eea5962ac731ac90cc6c8fdc9a8.avif?t=1656313626\" width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >怪物</h2>每个怪物都拥有自己独特的技能，精英和领主怪物则拥有更多更强的技能，仔细观察，不然也许一只小怪物也能让你翻车<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355440/extras/66a50dcb608d2d4aa9129f85d85322e9.avif?t=1656313626\" width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精通</h2>每次通关后你可以获得一定的精通点数，通过加点你可以自行定制你的游戏流程来获得更舒适或更有挑战性的游戏体验<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355440/extras/94db695cfa1873dcd19cfdffadea3303.avif?t=1656313626\" width=800 height=450 /></span>",
